name: State | 06 Late at Night
description:
Late at Night is an ode to late nights spent with your significant other or close friends and family. It serves as a sense of release.

It is the sixth song from the debut album, State. The work and animations featured in the State series represent the rebirth as an artist and is the culmination of five years of work. The album and animated series allowed a sense of liberation to create and make the Bases project what it is today. This work serves as the foundation. 

This is the sixth animation in the series and it will not be minted elsewhere. 

Music by Darryl Kirchner 
Artwork and Animation by Darryl Kirchner
